{"tid":1745151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國戰線】幫美籍黑警報稅","createTime":"2019-11-22T05:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T05:56:35.000Z","uid":28843,"like":107,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"9538c7b6d3bc84f47f4fc14e76f36896e1fe4bb3","tid":1745151,"uid":28843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"黑警唔好以為真係做乜都可以有持無恐<br />\n尤其是雙重國籍嗰啲，唔篤你地出嚟都唔係人<br />\n<br />\n其他國籍唔知，但有美國籍（綠卡或有PASSPORT）嘅，就算響香港住，一樣要報稅！<br />\n就算GREEN OBJECTS 同WHITE OBJECTS搵唔到咁多，但規矩上一樣要報。車位收租、津貼、中六合彩，中馬，收獎金獎品，劏房收租都要報！<br />\n唔交稅犯法，唔報稅一樣犯法。張五常就係逃稅被美國政府通緝，唔敢再返去！<br />\n<br />\n如果你識D狗或狗乸、狗仔、狗女、狗媽、狗爸有美籍嘅，溫馨提示一下美國IRS，有美國籍公民居民海外逃稅，提供英文全名+生日日期就夠做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者去Internal Revenue Service DOWNLOAD張FORM F3949A，知道幾多盡填，唔想填FORM嘅直接留言或者 tg pm有專人為你服務。講多句，本來成功舉報而政府又收得番稅會有獎金，我唔知非居民有無得收，但呢張FORM係俾匿名人唔駛要獎金嘅用，費事又俾人誤會我地收美金做嘢啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班美籍狗返唔到去咪留香港繼續求神拜佛世世代代有狗做囉。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTg: TeleGo"},{"pid":"cf506327afc20e0d83c0565b9daaffdbc1fc0d8d","tid":1745151,"uid":254504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"gogogi"},{"pid":"179443925da7f4bbc4ee5b5e4b1d709871ca5db3","tid":1745151,"uid":84529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e876317551d4e82a1b1c5f4e501af01d63959257","tid":1745151,"uid":43665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:36:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"329747404e56b3